name: Punk Ape Pixel Club
description:
Punk Ape Pixel Club OG (PAPC-OG) SOLD OUT.
Is a collection of 368 unique and collectable Punk themed Apes on the Ethereum blockchain.

A hybrid collection of two of the most iconic projects in the NFT space. Harnessing the pixelated power of Crypto Punks forged with BAYC DNA, PAPC is a new breed of NFT. Pixelated Primates.

Driven by evolution.
